hh3cDot11LIC.name: hh3cDot11LIC

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

hh3cDot11LIC.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip: 100085
hh3cDot11LIC.description: This MIB provides information for WLAN license configuration in AC. GLOSSARY IEEE 802.11 Standard to encourage interoperability among wireless networking equipment. Access point (AP) Transmitter/receiver (transceiver) device that commonly connects and transports data between a wireless network and a wired network. Access control (AC) To control and manage multi-APs, it will bridge wireless and wired network. Fit AP Applied in the enterprise environment, it will work under the control and management from AC. Control And Provisioning of Wireless Access Points Protocol The short name of protocol is CAPWAP. AC will control and manage AP by CAPWAP tunnel protocol defined by IETF. Also, a data tunnel will be set up between AC and AP. Basic Service Set The IEEE 802.11 BSS of an AP comprises of the stations directly associating with the AP. It will be identified by BSSID.

hh3cDot11LicApNumGroupSupport.name: hh3cDot11LicApNumGroupSupport
hh3cDot11LicApNumGroupSupport.description: Represents support hh3cDot11LicApNumGroup 'ture': device spport hh3cDot11LicApNumGroup. 'false': device not spport hh3cDot11LicApNumGroupp.

hh3cDot11LICDefautAPNumPermit.name: hh3cDot11LICDefautAPNumPermit
hh3cDot11LICDefautAPNumPermit.description: Represents the number of AP connection permitted for one AC without license.

hh3cDot11LICCurrentAPNumPermit.name: hh3cDot11LICCurrentAPNumPermit
hh3cDot11LICCurrentAPNumPermit.description: Represents the total number of AP connection permitted for one AC, include default number and the licenses that installed.

hh3cDot11LICMaxAPNumPermit.name: hh3cDot11LICMaxAPNumPermit
hh3cDot11LICMaxAPNumPermit.description: Represents the maximum number of AP to support connection permitted for one AC, include default number and full licenses.

hh3cDot11LICApNumLicEntry.name: hh3cDot11LICApNumLicEntry

hh3cDot11LICApNum.name: hh3cDot11LICApNum

hh3cDot11LICFeatureAttrTable.name: hh3cDot11LICFeatureAttrTable

hh3cDot11LICAttrDefVal.name: hh3cDot11LICAttrDefVal

hh3cDot11LICAttrMaxVal.name: hh3cDot11LICAttrMaxVal

hh3cDot11LICFeatureLicTable.name: hh3cDot11LICFeatureLicTable

hh3cDot11LICFeatureLicEntry.name: hh3cDot11LICFeatureLicEntry

hh3cDot11LICTypeName.name: hh3cDot11LICTypeName

hh3cDot11LICTimeLimit.name: hh3cDot11LICTimeLimit
